function info($str) { echo "INFO: $str\n"; }
function warn($str) { echo "WARNING: $str\n"; }
function err($str) { die("FATAL ERROR: $str\n"); }

@set_time_limit(0);

@header('Content-Type: text/plain');

chdir(__DIR__);
if (trim(@file_get_contents('oidplus_version.txt')) !== 'Revision 385') {
	err('This update can only be applied to OIDplus version 2.0.0.385!');
}

if (version_compare(PHP_VERSION, '7.0.0') < 0) {
	err('You need PHP Version 7.0 to update to this version');
}

// File added: .buildpath
function writefile_1() {
	@$fp = fopen('.buildpath', 'w');
	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('PD94bWwgdmVyc2lvbj0iMS4wIiBlbmNvZGluZz0iVVRGLTgiPz4NCjxidWlsZHBhdGg+DQoJPGJ1aWxkcGF0aGVudHJ5IGtpbmQ9InNyYyIgcGF0aD0iIi8+DQoJPGJ1aWxkcGF0aGVudHJ5IGtpbmQ9ImNvbiIgcGF0aD0ib3JnLmVjbGlwc2UucGhwLmNvcmUuTEFO'));
	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('R1VBR0UiLz4NCjwvYnVpbGRwYXRoPg0K'));
	@fclose($fp);
}
if (is_file('.buildpath') && (sha1_file('.buildpath') != '2a8553304ffa895aab18967d0467a0536d47499e')) {
	warn('File was created by someone else. Will overwrite the changes now: .buildpath');
	$tmp = pathinfo('.buildpath');
	$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('.buildpath')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
	warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
	if (!@copy('.buildpath', $backup_name)) {
		warn('Creation of backup failed');
	}
}
writefile_1();
if (!is_file('.buildpath')) {
	warn('File cannot be created (not existing): .buildpath');
} else if (sha1_file('.buildpath') != '2a8553304ffa895aab18967d0467a0536d47499e') {
	warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): .buildpath');
} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('.buildpath', 0644)) {
	warn('Could not change file permissions of .buildpath');
}

if (!is_file('dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps');
	writefile_12();
	if (!is_file('dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps');
	} else if (sha1_file('dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps') != 'aa4738ea4a1198d8e9a33ed917e1f86202e398ea') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps', 0755)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps') !== 'aa4738ea4a1198d8e9a33ed917e1f86202e398ea') {
		if (@sha1_file('dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps') !== '823d9cc19c92525deef183cb9c43119c784ca267') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps');
			$tmp = pathinfo('dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_12();
		if (@sha1_file('dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps') !== 'aa4738ea4a1198d8e9a33ed917e1f86202e398ea') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps');
	writefile_13();
	if (!is_file('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps');
	} else if (sha1_file('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps') != '6389d87a0595a19eb25ca3d273b4bcebc87bc787') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps', 0755)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps') !== '6389d87a0595a19eb25ca3d273b4bcebc87bc787') {
		if (@sha1_file('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps') !== 'cebccd139595e450c48b7f5131101e731a75e9a3') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps');
			$tmp = pathinfo('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_13();
		if (@sha1_file('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps') !== '6389d87a0595a19eb25ca3d273b4bcebc87bc787') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
	writefile_14();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php') != '4aad508922a72cc9377b524dd616ad6737ec242e') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php') !== '4aad508922a72cc9377b524dd616ad6737ec242e') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php') !== 'c612c74a1c8e6177f0f61df0bfd4a40a4d244f3d') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_14();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php') !== '4aad508922a72cc9377b524dd616ad6737ec242e') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php');
	writefile_15();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php') != '5e20d524dc763a5df32b74b5df4b6459f29a4fdb') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php') !== '5e20d524dc763a5df32b74b5df4b6459f29a4fdb') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php') !== '46deadfb25f8336fe566a28a3595dbe638b7f32e') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_15();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php') !== '5e20d524dc763a5df32b74b5df4b6459f29a4fdb') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('includes/classes/SecureMailer.class.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/classes/SecureMailer.class.php');
	writefile_18();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/SecureMailer.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/SecureMailer.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/SecureMailer.class.php') != '93eab3425696191c1bcc9c4ad4f1411fb88ab7e2') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/SecureMailer.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/SecureMailer.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/SecureMailer.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/SecureMailer.class.php') !== '93eab3425696191c1bcc9c4ad4f1411fb88ab7e2') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/SecureMailer.class.php') !== '7a8f60b68d9573f6935e9996c1363a413b44ad40') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/SecureMailer.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/SecureMailer.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/SecureMailer.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/SecureMailer.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_18();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/SecureMailer.class.php') !== '93eab3425696191c1bcc9c4ad4f1411fb88ab7e2') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/SecureMailer.class.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('includes/classes/http_class.class.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/classes/http_class.class.php');
	writefile_19();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/http_class.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/http_class.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/http_class.class.php') != '6808b0f8551bdaff5d01c780f5cc66c4c1bbf3a9') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/http_class.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/http_class.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/http_class.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/http_class.class.php') !== '6808b0f8551bdaff5d01c780f5cc66c4c1bbf3a9') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/http_class.class.php') !== '15842253d4896b30a30ac611279ed95ca0fe1dd1') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/http_class.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/http_class.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/http_class.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/http_class.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_19();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/http_class.class.php') !== '6808b0f8551bdaff5d01c780f5cc66c4c1bbf3a9') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/http_class.class.php');
		}
	}
}

			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/db_updates/update203.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/db_updates/update203.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_24();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/db_updates/update203.inc.php') !== '0f7e9a3c4de8e8d3e95f58ecc1271ada2147374f') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/db_updates/update203.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/functions.inc.php');
	writefile_25();
	if (!is_file('includes/functions.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/functions.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/functions.inc.php') != '70f21da79d1f3defc3ec1161edd96c8646f42874') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/functions.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/functions.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/functions.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/functions.inc.php') !== '70f21da79d1f3defc3ec1161edd96c8646f42874') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/functions.inc.php') !== 'b93f0909b41296e5697398ee3a9d3e388ddaa7b5') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/functions.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/functions.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/functions.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/functions.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_25();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/functions.inc.php') !== '70f21da79d1f3defc3ec1161edd96c8646f42874') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/functions.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

	@fclose($fp);
}
if (!is_file('includes/gmp_supplement.inc.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/gmp_supplement.inc.php');
	writefile_26();
	if (!is_file('includes/gmp_supplement.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/gmp_supplement.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/gmp_supplement.inc.php') != '499490a9c2dbf47a46c8f6bdfa719f11342928d0') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/gmp_supplement.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/gmp_supplement.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/gmp_supplement.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/gmp_supplement.inc.php') !== '499490a9c2dbf47a46c8f6bdfa719f11342928d0') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/gmp_supplement.inc.php') !== 'c4c997987316cbd5d994050885b57f2faf51ef14') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/gmp_supplement.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/gmp_supplement.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/gmp_supplement.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/gmp_supplement.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_26();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/gmp_supplement.inc.php') !== '499490a9c2dbf47a46c8f6bdfa719f11342928d0') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/gmp_supplement.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('includes/oid_utils.inc.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/oid_utils.inc.php');
	writefile_27();
	if (!is_file('includes/oid_utils.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/oid_utils.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/oid_utils.inc.php') != '0f97013a0eb4c5285d7b965b5850d8a6d271c077') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/oid_utils.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/oid_utils.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/oid_utils.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/oid_utils.inc.php') !== '0f97013a0eb4c5285d7b965b5850d8a6d271c077') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/oid_utils.inc.php') !== '084805c673620f0f1624ebdd0ea44cce474d4b0b') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/oid_utils.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/oid_utils.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/oid_utils.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/oid_utils.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_27();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/oid_utils.inc.php') !== '0f97013a0eb4c5285d7b965b5850d8a6d271c077') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/oid_utils.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('plugins/language/dede/messages.xml')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/language/dede/messages.xml');
	writefile_55();
	if (!is_file('plugins/language/dede/messages.xml')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/language/dede/messages.xml');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/language/dede/messages.xml') != '0d5cb6e302615153081eebe8c5595efda3da8aa3') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/language/dede/messages.xml');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/language/dede/messages.xml', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/language/dede/messages.xml');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/language/dede/messages.xml') !== '0d5cb6e302615153081eebe8c5595efda3da8aa3') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/language/dede/messages.xml') !== '4555fffeebbc7d77ca662a6e1123316b98affc0f') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/language/dede/messages.xml');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/language/dede/messages.xml');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/language/dede/messages.xml')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/language/dede/messages.xml', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_55();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/language/dede/messages.xml') !== '0d5cb6e302615153081eebe8c5595efda3da8aa3') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/language/dede/messages.xml');
		}
	}
}

			if (!@copy('plugins/objectTypes/other/manifest.xml', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_71();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/objectTypes/other/manifest.xml') !== '4ba4a9010c59e192dad83c7f7e3f5c2084ff142d') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/objectTypes/other/manifest.xml');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php');
	writefile_84();
	if (!is_file('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php') != 'e6500c587ef2be13ec8e3d1c892844b9542dedf2') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php') !== 'e6500c587ef2be13ec8e3d1c892844b9542dedf2') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php') !== 'ecc1f2d0a6a6fbc3bc5f17c5a68b0c2e0daef037') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_84();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php') !== 'e6500c587ef2be13ec8e3d1c892844b9542dedf2') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('plugins/publicPages/300_search/manifest.xml')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/publicPages/300_search/manifest.xml');
	writefile_89();
	if (!is_file('plugins/publicPages/300_search/manifest.xml')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/publicPages/300_search/manifest.xml');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/300_search/manifest.xml') != '15db3fa577adebaaf01bd5bc011c8da1add3ce6d') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/publicPages/300_search/manifest.xml');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/publicPages/300_search/manifest.xml', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/publicPages/300_search/manifest.xml');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/300_search/manifest.xml') !== '15db3fa577adebaaf01bd5bc011c8da1add3ce6d') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/300_search/manifest.xml') !== '1565ba3be206ba171744a1a969f9727b3b2f05f3') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/publicPages/300_search/manifest.xml');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/publicPages/300_search/manifest.xml');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/publicPages/300_search/manifest.xml')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/publicPages/300_search/manifest.xml', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_89();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/300_search/manifest.xml') !== '15db3fa577adebaaf01bd5bc011c8da1add3ce6d') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/publicPages/300_search/manifest.xml');
		}
	}
}

	@fclose($fp);
}
if (!is_file('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements$dede.html')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: res/OIDplus/acknowledgements$dede.html');
	writefile_105();
	if (!is_file('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements$dede.html')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): res/OIDplus/acknowledgements$dede.html');
	} else if (sha1_file('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements$dede.html') != 'd11715e707c2ce2ae5dc7a6419b9649f54485727') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): res/OIDplus/acknowledgements$dede.html');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements$dede.html', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of res/OIDplus/acknowledgements$dede.html');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements$dede.html') !== 'd11715e707c2ce2ae5dc7a6419b9649f54485727') {
		if (@sha1_file('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements$dede.html') !== '6e182c2450e7424f7d7148be9f463aad80a6e23b') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: res/OIDplus/acknowledgements$dede.html');
			$tmp = pathinfo('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements$dede.html');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements$dede.html')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements$dede.html', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_105();
		if (@sha1_file('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements$dede.html') !== 'd11715e707c2ce2ae5dc7a6419b9649f54485727') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): res/OIDplus/acknowledgements$dede.html');
		}
	}
}

	@fclose($fp);
}
if (!is_file('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html');
	writefile_106();
	if (!is_file('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html');
	} else if (sha1_file('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html') != '132d71e81c537343fa5d38d1ab31de195513bb5c') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html') !== '132d71e81c537343fa5d38d1ab31de195513bb5c') {
		if (@sha1_file('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html') !== '252009260ea841fd50c107be0d10a8e6973ddd92') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html');
			$tmp = pathinfo('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_106();
		if (@sha1_file('res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html') !== '132d71e81c537343fa5d38d1ab31de195513bb5c') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): res/OIDplus/acknowledgements.html');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html');
	writefile_107();
	if (!is_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html');
	} else if (sha1_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html') != '413596a3e0cc83ccf337bd98c0c220884c9a135c') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html') !== '413596a3e0cc83ccf337bd98c0c220884c9a135c') {
		if (@sha1_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html') !== 'f25178cf4d790f5a7f2a5bbb49ff271230be6142') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html');
			$tmp = pathinfo('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_107();
		if (@sha1_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html') !== '413596a3e0cc83ccf337bd98c0c220884c9a135c') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation$dede.html');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html');
	writefile_108();
	if (!is_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html');
	} else if (sha1_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html') != '4ee5ec2e6ef710047c91cf273a841919b22dac7a') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html') !== '4ee5ec2e6ef710047c91cf273a841919b22dac7a') {
		if (@sha1_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html') !== 'b18ce3253c59ae965bdba83444070da0ac88ed27') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html');
			$tmp = pathinfo('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_108();
		if (@sha1_file('res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html') !== '4ee5ec2e6ef710047c91cf273a841919b22dac7a') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): res/OIDplus/privacy_documentation.html');
		}
	}
}


file_put_contents('oidplus_version.txt', "Revision 386\n");
if (trim(@file_get_contents('oidplus_version.txt')) !== 'Revision 386') err('Could not write to oidplus_version.txt!');


echo 'DONE'; // This exact string will be compared in Update v3

@unlink(__FILE__);
if (is_file(__FILE__)) warn('Could not delete '.basename(__FILE__).'! Please delete it manually');
